OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain in the east soon clearing.
OL,6,FThen sunny spells and scattered
OL,7,Fshowers, these will be occasionally
OL,8,Fheavy by afternoon with a risk of
OL,9,Fhail. Blustery southwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be a rather cloudy
OL,12,Fevening with showers, some of these
OL,13,Fheavy at first. Further showery
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain will spread in from
OL,15,Fthe west through the early hours.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FA rather cloudy day with
OL,18,Fscattered showers, occasionally heavy
OL,19,Fat times. Some sunnier spells,
OL,20,Fespecially early and late in the day.
OL,21,FBreezy, especially around coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
